Windows Registry Editor Version 5.00

; Resets the " - Shortcut" text that is appended to shortcuts to default

; 1. Reset the legacy binary 'link' value to default
[HKEY_CURRENT_USER\Software\Microsoft\Windows\CurrentVersion\Explorer]
"link"=hex:1e,00,00,00

; Default (Windows handles this automatically; no manual entry normally exists)
; To restore default behavior, delete the Custom NamingTemplates key:
[-HKEY_CURRENT_USER\Software\Microsoft\Windows\CurrentVersion\Explorer\NamingTemplates]
